Pattern 3: Operators as control flow
============================================================

(a + b) fields: ['answer', 'cons']
(a | None) -> {'answer': 'A'}
(None | b) -> {'cons': 'B'}
(a & None) -> None
(a ^ None) is not None -> True
(a ^ b) is None      -> True
(~a) -> None
